text: ❤️❤️❤️ I attended the service on Sunday 9AM. People here are so welcome and loving.

A lively Eastern Orthodox parish that serves Divine Liturgy every Sunday at 9am. There is also Virgil on Saturdays, usually at 5pm.

It is recommended for Men to come in long pants and covered shoes. Women are recommended to bring head covering and dress modestly.
Nice little parish for Eastern Orthodox Christians.
Great place! This is where I returned back to true faith! It is like a big family, everyone cares for each other.))
I owe much of my positive developments to this parish.
